{"tid":2017110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捷克參議院通過決議 支持台灣參與WHO","createTime":"2020-05-15T02:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T02:27:02.000Z","uid":357030,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"04c9b731a38c46dcd1d2336ede4acd66f04ca92a","tid":2017110,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:00:39.000Z","msg":"捷克參議院兩個委員會13日創捷克國會首例，分別通過決議案，建議世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長邀請台灣參與世界衛生大會（WHA），並籲請捷克政府支持台灣參與WHO。<br />\n<br />\nWHA將於18至19日以視訊會議形式舉行，台灣迄今未接獲與會邀請函。台灣曾在2009至2016年連續8年期間受WHO秘書長邀請，以觀察員身分與會。不過，WHO秘書處近日屢以會員國「缺乏政治共識」為由，說明今年無法邀請台灣參與WHA。<br />\n<br />\n外交部今天晚間發布新聞稿指出，捷克參議院「外交、國防暨安全委員會」及「衛生暨社會政策委員會」13日分別通過決議案，支持台灣參與WHO及WHA，並籲請捷克政府支持。此為捷克國會相關委員會近年來首度通過決議案支持台灣參與WHO，甚具意義。<br />\n<br />\n外交部表示，決議案要點包括台灣參與WHO的權利長期遭剝奪，這違反國際醫衛社群尊重多元、道德及專業的價值觀；台灣對抗武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情成效顯著，善用台灣經驗、將台灣納入全球公衛體系對公眾有利；建議WHO秘書長邀請台灣參與今年的WHA，以符合WHO「全民均健」（Health for All）原則；以及籲請捷克政府支持台灣參與WHO。<br />\n<br />\n外交部指出，決議案由友台的捷克參議院「外交、國防暨安全委員會」主席費雪（Pavel Fischer），以及「衛生暨社會政策委員會」主席賀社（Marek Hil&scaron;er）發起，獲委員會成員高度支持，充分展現捷克國會對台灣的堅定友誼。<br />\n<br />\n外交部對此表示誠摯感謝，並期待WHO傾聽各界民意，基於科學專業，以務實態度回應，而不應任由特定會員國進行政治操作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120940/4564771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120940%2F4564771&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=59b4183c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120940/4564771</a>"},{"pid":"f1b8291bed3c3044d26a83ba4968b17a14391275","tid":2017110,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nTaiwan No.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1677212a7e5d67268e383f8a5f0629db161308","tid":2017110,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推呀"},{"pid":"4949e2fc52d614fe7d0cd0fc27db0cb0dae0dd71","tid":2017110,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:09:15.000Z","msg":"加埋美國支持應該好快入who"},{"pid":"f98be938dd6bd6a2d87b1232009343be1189de2d","tid":2017110,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"希望snowball effect其他人跟機"},{"pid":"b0c69ccf9547f3f0b074332c2bb86a3de4b2b48a","tid":2017110,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ugxTzK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ugxTzK.png&h=9d80b016&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582381334e8516da9a6417099a9486459c8df507","tid":2017110,"uid":298796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:54:34.000Z","msg":"小英政府要多做外交，最好同倒歐洲，甚至俄國傾倒計，就嚇死支共"},{"pid":"20f62634e5b51f1502104c9df10b42da80193eff","tid":2017110,"uid":344425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"查實捷克點解同台灣咁friend？之前有咩淵源？"},{"pid":"a26c38c544d91fb46f003d99d75daa8c567870b6","tid":2017110,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f62634e5b51f1502104c9df10b42da80193eff","tid":2017110,"uid":344425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"查實捷克點解同台灣咁friend？之前有咩淵源？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T04:53:07.000Z","msg":"布拉格市長 (海盜黨) 係反共反支 一上任就開始靠攏台灣<br />\n早排同台北結為姊妹城市 然後同好似上海解除姊妹城市關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cda0b3c5c0e05dc09d08a79c0110dba6c484790","tid":2017110,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"結果好似都幫唔到台灣o的乜o野"},{"pid":"acec1e6a3c91cbbc881e139a32e072744361c1c5"